CycUp is a verified, student-only digital marketplace designed to solve a recurring and costly problem faced by university students in Finland, particularly international students. CycUp allows students to register with their official university email addresses, instantly creating a trusted, closed community. The platform enables students to buy, sell, rent, or give away second-hand items easily from the moment they arrive, reducing living costs,
preventing waste, and supporting a circular campus economy. Whether you just arrived or are preparing to leave campus, Cycup is for you!
